public class FibonacciActionServer
extends DefaultActionServer<org.ros.message.actionlib_tutorials.FibonacciActionFeedback,org.ros.message.actionlib_tutorials.FibonacciActionGoal,org.ros.message.actionlib_tutorials.FibonacciActionResult,org.ros.message.actionlib_tutorials.FibonacciFeedback,org.ros.message.actionlib_tutorials.FibonacciGoal,org.ros.message.actionlib_tutorials.FibonacciResult>

The FibonacciActionServer is a specialized DefaultActionServer that offers services related to the Fibonacci action. The FibonacciActionServer completely hides the Generics approach of the DefaultActionServer's implementation.
